**Control:**
- `<Space>ds` - Start debugging
- `<Space>dc` - Continue
- `<Space>dp` - Pause
- `<Space>dr` - Restart
- `<Space>dq` - Quit/Stop

**Stepping:**
- `<Space>do` - Step Over
- `<Space>di` - Step Into  
- `<Space>dO` - Step Out

**Breakpoints:**
- `<Space>db` - Toggle breakpoint
- `<Space>dB` - Conditional breakpoint
- `<Space>dl` - Toggle logpoint

**Debug UI:**
- `<Space>dv` - Focus variables
- `<Space>dw` - Focus watch
- `<Space>dk` - Focus call stack
- `<Space>dh` - Show debug hover

